{
 "name": "RPlog_Not_My_Kind_of_Archaeology_Kithan_Lost_Her_Marbles",
 "title": "Not My Kind of Archaeology: Kithan Lost Her Marbles",
 "summary": "The excitable Squib Kithan bursts into Senator Tokoga's office in a panic, clutching a dark robe and babbling about a relic, magnacuffs, and a sinister scene she witnessed at the starport. Calming her, Tokoga coaxes out a fragmentary story of a wheezing 'asthma' voice over a holoemitter, a Jedi apprentice named Jan who refused to be led astray, and Kithan throwing her beloved marbles at a Sith before her memory goes inexplicably blank. She presents an amulet bearing the seal of the New Sith Order, which Tokoga resolves to send to the Jedi Archives for identification. After reassuring the worried Squib that she did the right thing, the Senator playfully bargains with her -- in Squibbian -- trading a large bag to replace her lost marbles for the amulet, and arranges for her to speak with Commander Cen and the Jedi.",
